Package de.dedede.model.data.dtos

Class UserDto

java.lang.Object
de.dedede.model.data.dtos.UserDto
public class UserDto extends Object
This DTO (data transfer object) is responsible for aggregating and encapsulating data about a user for transfer.

See the UserDao class to which this DTO is passed.

Author:
Sergei Pravdin

    • getLendingPeriod

      public java.time.Duration getLendingPeriod()
      Fetches a lending period that the administrator has privately set for the user. This lending period overrides the global lending period in the application, but does not override the private lending period of the medium.
      Returns:
      A lending period for the user.
